summary:
Lembac services international is an open-innovation company that buys and sells things for local communities in Africa and Europe. A key feature of Lembac Services International is its partnership model with customers and investors around the globe. It is this kind of cross-fertilization that enables Lembac Services International to tune its marketing strategy to community need.


For more information please visite our website:
http://www.lembacservicesint.com
